\layout Standard

Example: typing 
\family typewriter 
'%cd mydir'
\family default 
 (without the quotes) changes you working directory to 
\family typewriter 
'mydir'
\family default 
, if it exists.
\layout Standard

If you have 'automagic' enabled (in your 
\family typewriter 
ipythonrc
\family default 
