\newline 
$endif
\layout Standard

Note that there are 4 spaces between the quote marks after 
\family typewriter 
"M-i"
\family default 
 above.
\layout Standard


\series bold 
Warning:
\series default 
 this feature is ON by default, but it can cause problems with the pasting
